    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      private boolean essential
      This variable is set to 1 to indicate that the associated property is essential to the item, otherwise it is non-essential.
      private int propertyIndex
      The variable is either 0 indicating that no property is associated (the essential indicator shall also be 0), or is the 1-based index of the associated property box in the ItemPropertyContainerBox contained in the same ItemPropertiesBox.
